Bremen midfielder Marko Marin, the Premier League club said on
its website.  The teams agreed to an undisclosed fee and the 23-year-old
Marin will join Chelsea in the summer, the club said.  Marin has 12 goals in 87 Bundesliga games since joining
Bremen from Monchengladbach in 2009. Heâ€™s also made 16
